premise_source_doc_sentence: José Aldo da Silva Oliveira Junior  (  -LSB- ʒoˈzɛ ˈaldu -RSB- ; born September 9 , 1986  )  is a Brazilian mixed martial artist in the Ultimate Fighting Championship and the UFC Featherweight Champion , currently in his second reign .
